{"tid":1381792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳辦的3重點，4堅持講咩!","createTime":"2019-07-29T10:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:28:51.000Z","uid":284695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13b54a8f4b0e6f2bd0f2e115f5e6794d50176cee","tid":1381792,"uid":284695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiOHKjD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiOHKjD.png&h=78c59627&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對於共產黨的八股文，後生仔睇唔明係應該嘅，因為對象係果的聽阿爺吩咐的奴才，我試下翻譯成人話，讓大家易於理解:<br />\n<br />\n三大重點: <br />\n1) 阿爺吹雞，號召所有保皇黨歸位，唔好龜縮，唔好轉軚，一定要死撐，撐到底。<br />\n2) 將任何唔肯跪底嘅示威人士，拉晒去坐監。<br />\n3) 如果仲有唔怕死嘅，等坐洗頭艇。<br />\n<br />\n四大堅持:<br />\n1) 堅持林鄭唔準辭職，想坐佢位嘅要等多陣。<br />\n2) 堅持警察唔準留手，阿爺撐你，張建宗再阿芝阿佐就連佢都無運行。<br />\n3) 堅持所有黑勢力出動打擊示威者，拉唔晒都要打殘你。<br />\n4) 堅持愛國人士必須出錢出力，完成以上任務。<br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n佢要晒冷，佢覺得贏硬，咁大家睇下點囉!"},{"pid":"491a567dd3fad8a132f60ed223616b6484213ce9","tid":1381792,"uid":29689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9Shygz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9Shygz.png&h=bcf7410c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特登搵張殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前為選票講錯野嗰啲建制仲唔快啲出來嚴正聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eade47020305ba4a47ef050c95293c27f59f120","tid":1381792,"uid":284695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"491a567dd3fad8a132f60ed223616b6484213ce9","tid":1381792,"uid":29689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9Shygz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9Shygz.png&h=bcf7410c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特登搵張殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前為選票講錯野嗰啲建制仲唔快啲出來嚴正聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\"